{"tid":1498660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[WeConnect] 袋鼠國學生想聽到你地嘅聲音","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T04:48:10.000Z","uid":107693,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"036b295795ab549989e454332db7ce37dd07eb95","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"呢班人係袋鼠國usyd 學生，<br />\n佢地會喺8.30 喺校內舉辦一場短程嘅遊行，<br />\n目的係比更多人知道香港依家經歷緊嘅事。<br />\n但因為之前喺袋鼠國發生左唔少衝突事件，<br />\n佢地知道好多人都唔敢講佢地對呢事嘅睇法，<br />\n所以佢地想聽下大家發夢嘅見聞同心路歷程，<br />\n會喺遊行當日讀出嚟，或者放落連儂牆度。<br />\n<br />\n以下喺佢地嘅google form，一切匿名處理，<br />\n但希望大家用英文寫，<br />\n因為佢地當中大部分唔識睇中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/o9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fo9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=218f8775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/o9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8</a><br />\n<br />\n我明白大家可能會有顧慮，唔填表都唔緊要！<br />\n喺度寫低都可以架<br />\n我可以轉告佢地或者幫手翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n辛苦曬各位手足，<br />\n人在異地，無辦法同你地並肩作戰，<br />\n一路睇住香港發生嘅事，<br />\n真係好無力、好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地一直唔放棄，<br />\n各地留學生都會支持住你地，<br />\n記住要齊上齊落，好好保護自己。"},{"pid":"119c75e1cc1d1af353d03086236fe6ca4a9ebb0d","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"附上佢地嘅原文<br />\n<br />\nHello LIHKG, I am one of the organisers for a protest to raise awareness about the movement in HK at the University of Sydney, Australia. As a HK Aussie, the recent events that have happened in Australian campuses has highlighted the fact that many students, both HKers and Chinese mainlanders, are unable to openly support the movement due to fears of being harassed. Not only are we interested in giving a voice to those who are too afraid of speaking out, but also reaching out to the international community, in particular, Hong Kong locals.<br />\nIf you are interested in providing a statement that may be read out on the day of the protest or posted on a new Lennon Wall, please use the following Google Form.<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/o9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fo9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=218f8775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/o9Rwk9gQsdrEMJ3b8</a><br />\n<br />\nHere is a link to the protest event details if you are interested.https://<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/events/2670127636385037/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2670127636385037%2F&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b030bbee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/events/2670127636385037/</a>"},{"pid":"0b61a74360fdbe8edc7407e29e550bcc36509646","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c2cfb76709c5b245cc75015b1bd93eaffd1f40d","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db790a966b86e5ac0bd2927cd5e100cd6a1d6d07","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee33986b287e1b90e57337fff41ddd120fafacd4","tid":1498660,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"返屋企填"},{"pid":"f69acf086d1f0e889832a5a249ffa1a65e4d4607","tid":1498660,"uid":107693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:13:08.000Z